 549         }

 555         {

 557         }

 559         {

 562         public override Node* Clone(CloneContext& cloneContext) const
 563         {

 575         {

 579             bool convertExternal = ModuleId() == writer.SpanConversionModuleId();
 580             writer.Write(whileSpan, convertExternal);
 581             writer.Write(leftParenSpan, convertExternal);
 582             writer.Write(rightParenSpan, convertExternal);

 584         public override void Read(AstReader& reader)

 589             condition.Reset(reader.ReadNode());
 590             condition->SetParent(this);
 591             whileSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 592             leftParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 593             rightParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 594         }

 601     public class ForStatementNode : StatementNode
 602     {
 603         public nothrow ForStatementNode(const System.Lex.Span& span_, const Uuid& moduleId_) : 
 604             base(NodeType.forStatementNode, span_, moduleId_), initS(), condition(), loopS(), actionS()
 605         {
 606         }
 607         public nothrow ForStatementNode(const System.Lex.Span& span_, const Uuid& moduleId_, StatementNode* initS_, Node* condition_, StatementNode* loopS_, StatementNode* actionS_) : 
 608             base(NodeType.forStatementNode, span_, moduleId_), initS(initS_), condition(condition_), loopS(loopS_), actionS(actionS_)
 609         {
 610             initS->SetParent(this);
 611             if (!condition.IsNull())
 612             {
 613                 condition->SetParent(this);
 614             }
 615             loopS->SetParent(this);
 616             actionS->SetParent(this);
 617         }
 618         public nothrow const StatementNode* InitS() const

 620             return initS.Get();
 621         }

 650         public nothrow void SetLeftParenSpan(const System.Lex.Span& leftParenSpan_)

 653         }
 654         public nothrow const System.Lex.Span& LeftParenSpan() const
 655         {

 657         }
 658         public nothrow void SetRightParenSpan(const System.Lex.Span& rightParenSpan_)
 659         {

 661         }

 663         {
 664             return rightParenSpan;
 665         }
 666         public override nothrow bool IsBreakEnclosingStatementNode() const
 667         {
 668             return true;
 669         }
 670         public override nothrow bool IsContinueEnclosingStatementNode() const
 671         {
 672             return true;
 673         }
 674         public override Node* Clone(CloneContext& cloneContext) const
 675         {
 676             Node* clonedCondition = null;
 677             if (!condition.IsNull())
 678             {
 679                 clonedCondition = condition->Clone(cloneContext);
 680             }
 681             ForStatementNode* clone = new ForStatementNode(GetSpan(), ModuleId(), cast<StatementNode*>(initS->Clone(cloneContext)), clonedCondition, cast<StatementNode*>(loopS->Clone(cloneContext)), cast<StatementNode*>(actionS->Clone(cloneContext)));
 682             clone->SetLeftParenSpan(leftParenSpan);
 683             clone->SetRightParenSpan(rightParenSpan);
 684             return clone;
 685         }
 686         public override void Accept(Visitor& visitor)
 687         {
 688             visitor.Visit(*this);
 689         }
 690         public override nothrow void Write(AstWriter& writer)
 691         {
 692             base->Write(writer);
 693             writer.Write(initS.Get());
 694             bool hasCondition = condition != null;
 695             writer.GetBinaryWriter().Write(hasCondition);
 696             if (hasCondition)
 697             {
 698                 writer.Write(condition.Get());
 699             }
 700             writer.Write(loopS.Get());
 701             writer.Write(actionS.Get());
 702             bool convertExternal = ModuleId() == writer.SpanConversionModuleId();
 703             writer.Write(leftParenSpan, convertExternal);
 704             writer.Write(rightParenSpan, convertExternal);
 705         }
 706         public override void Read(AstReader& reader)
 707         {
 708             base->Read(reader);
 709             initS.Reset(reader.ReadStatementNode());
 710             initS->SetParent(this);
 711             bool hasCondition = reader.GetBinaryReader().ReadBool();
 712             if (hasCondition)
 713             {
 714                 condition.Reset(reader.ReadNode());
 715                 condition->SetParent(this);
 716             }
 717             loopS.Reset(reader.ReadStatementNode());
 718             loopS->SetParent(this);
 719             actionS.Reset(reader.ReadStatementNode());
 720             actionS->SetParent(this);
 721             leftParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 722             rightParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
 723         }
 724         private UniquePtr<StatementNode> initS;
 725         private UniquePtr<Node> condition;
 726         private UniquePtr<StatementNode> loopS;
 727         private UniquePtr<StatementNode> actionS;
 728         private System.Lex.Span leftParenSpan;
 729         private System.Lex.Span rightParenSpan;
 730     }

1753             }

1784             if (hasId)
1785             {
1786                 id.Reset(reader.ReadIdentifierNode());
1787                 id->SetParent(this);
1788             }
1789             catchBlock.Reset(reader.ReadCompoundStatementNode());
1790             catchBlock->SetParent(this);
1791             leftParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
1792             rightParenSpan = reader.ReadSpan();
1793         }
